latestIgtvVideos.title: REDHOOD
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Once upon a time I was a child , when came out hot red saw the same shade on that woman's head.

That woman who was all I could picture at the moment , that woman who gave birth to another woman.

That woman carpet with the white coat and that woman crowned with the white cap. I felt welcomed coz it was all done by no one but a woman.

I was new, I was fresh but I was extensively soaked in that red.

The red with which the journey began and the red with which it has to end, it has to end~ not necessarily be a visible red but be a deep-dug invisible red.

As the attention is all thrown when it's tangible coz no one bothers to know the hidden cannibal, the cannibal~the monsters, all in human faces but far away as disasters, disasters to the Redhood aka Womanhood.

So do we take stand or fight back up? Shouldn't be the question , if, those with criticism, condemnation, allegation, judgments & character-assassination are left unquestioned.

It's easy said than done because when this heart steps for hope alll she could reach upto is none.

Why is it bothering to be a woman? Why does it have to be subjective to all the humans? 

The vagina who took birth didn't enter the world with the right, the right that these penises  think they have to label her as a whore~ A whore , a hooker, a slut , a slattern and even more.

And who do you think on Earth gets trapped in this shitty shore? Is it really us or you coz I highly doubt you , you , you and only you ,just you , all of you. 

It doesn't matter if you are man or a woman coz nobody has the right to slut-shame a Human!

And before leaving , do not mistaken me for promoting feminism because all I am talking about is humanism, humanism ~ I doubt if it's a word but it's high time now that it should be preferred.

.
.
